2.res: Alright. Getting Facts anime Cardcaptor Sakura.Cardcaptor Sakura is a Japanese shōjo manga series written and illustrated by the manga group Clamp. The manga was originally serialized in Nakayoshi from May 1996 to June 2000, and published in 12 tankōbon volumes by Kodansha from November 1996 to July 2000.
